sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    participant MS as MembershipStore
    participant MPS as MockPaymentService
    participant AS as AuthStore

    User->>MS: openUpgradeDialog("图生图")
    MS-->>User: 显示升级弹窗

    User->>MS: startCheckout("pro", "monthly")
    MS->>MS: 设置 checkoutPlan, isPaymentProcessing=true
    MS->>MPS: processPayment({tier:"pro", plan:"monthly"})
    MPS-->>MS: 1.5s后返回 {success:true}
    MS->>MS: 更新 quotaState.tier="pro", 更新 daily 额度
    MS->>AS: updateProfile({tier:"pro"})
    MS->>MS: isPaymentProcessing=false, checkoutPlan=null
    MS-->>User: 订阅成功，显示Pro徽章

---

    actor User2
    participant CP as CreationPanel
    participant QG as useQuotaGuard
    participant MS2 as MembershipStore
    participant GS as GenerationStore

    User2->>CP: 点击生成按钮
    CP->>QG: checkQuota(generationType)
    QG->>MS2: checkQuota("TEXT_TO_IMAGE")

    alt 额度充足
        MS2-->>QG: {allowed:true}
        QG-->>CP: 通过
        CP->>GS: startGeneration(type, prompt, config)
        GS->>MS2: consumeQuota("image")
        MS2->>MS2: daily.image.used++
    else 日额度不足
        MS2-->>QG: {allowed:false, reason:"daily_exhausted", suggestion:"upgrade_or_credits"}
        QG-->>CP: 拦截
        CP->>MS2: openUpgradeDialog("daily_exhausted")
    else 权限不足(如Free用图生图)
        MS2-->>QG: {allowed:false, reason:"tier_restricted", suggestion:"upgrade"}
        QG-->>CP: 拦截
        CP->>MS2: openUpgradeDialog("tier_restricted")
    end

---

    actor User3
    participant CP2 as CreationPanel
    participant IU as ImageUpload
    participant RS as ReferenceSlider
    participant QG2 as useQuotaGuard
    participant GS2 as GenerationStore
    participant MAS as MockAIService

    User3->>CP2: 选择「图生图」模式
    CP2->>IU: 渲染图片上传区域
    User3->>IU: 上传参考图
    IU->>IU: FileReader.readAsDataURL → base64
    IU-->>CP2: 设置 referenceImageUrl=base64

    CP2->>RS: 渲染参考强度滑块
    User3->>RS: 调整强度 0.3~1.0
    RS-->>CP2: 设置 referenceStrength=0.7

    User3->>CP2: 输入Prompt + 点击生成
    CP2->>QG2: checkQuota("IMAGE_TO_IMAGE")
    QG2-->>CP2: {allowed:true} (Pro+)
    CP2->>GS2: startGeneration("IMAGE_TO_IMAGE", prompt, {referenceImageUrl, referenceStrength, ...})
    GS2->>MAS: generateImage(prompt, config)
    MAS-->>GS2: 返回 task
    GS2->>GS2: 轮询 → 完成
    GS2-->>CP2: 跳转结果页
